article_title: How One Private Exchange Is Helping Employees Make Better Health Care Choices

article_metadata.description: Consumers have immense power in today’s marketplace. We’re using our mobile devices to browse, choose, and buy online like never before. We are quickly connecting to what we need, what we want, and what’s important in our lives – including the right health insurance.
